'''Georgia ''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to Bitlife in the May 10, 2020 update, alongside [[Algeria]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Bolivia]], [[Croatia]], [[Hungary]], [[Jordan]], [[Qatar]], [[Slovakia]], and [[Zimbabwe]]. The only default city is its capital, Tbilisi. However, cities of Poti and Batumi are available in [[DogLife]].

